.TH NDRZCC 1 "2026" "ndrzcc" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ndrzcc \- DCE/RPC NDR marshalling compiler
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ndrzcc
.I input.idl output.c output.h
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ndrzcc
compiles a pragmatic subset of the Microsoft Interface Definition Language
(MS-IDL) into C code implementing DCE/RPC NDR (Network Data Representation,
transfer syntax 8a885d04-1ceb-11c9-9fe8-08002b104860) marshalling and
unmarshalling, plus a per-operation dispatch table for use by a DCE/RPC
server over named pipes.
.PP
It is a sibling of
.BR xdrzcc (1)
and mirrors its architecture: a Flex/Bison front end builds an AST which a
code generator lowers to C, with the runtime support embedded into the
generated source so the output has no external dependency beyond libc and a
caller-supplied character-conversion context.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR xdrzcc (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Chimera-NAS Project Contributors.
